Overview : 
	 -> This repository contains the code for Reachinbox frontend App using React with Typescript for an assignment given by Reachinbox.

Technologies Used ( Frontend ) : 
	1.Typescript
	2.React
	3.Tailwind css

How to Run :
	-> Installation :
			Clone the repository: git clone https://github.com/astuteuttu/reachinbox-assignment.git
			Navigate to the project directory: cd reachinbox
			Install the dependencies: npm install
			Start the development server: npm run start
			Open your browser and visit: http://localhost:3000
	-> Features :
		Authentication
		Get Emails
		Post (send) Email
		Delete Email

Endpoints :
		All Emails : GET {{baseurl}}/onebox/list 
		All Emails from Onebox : GET {{baseurl}}/onebox/messages/:thread_id 
		Add Onebox Mail : POST {{baseurl}}/onebox/reply/:thread_id 
		Delete Email : DELETE {{baseurl}}/onebox/messages/:thread_id 
